#. (itstool) path: sect2/para
#: C/index.docbook:1145
msgid "When not pressing a key while dropping the selection, the default is to query for the action to be executed, i.e. copy, move or create a symbolic link. In the GNOME Commander options you can change that behavior to copy or to move the selection. See also under <xref linkend=\"gnome-commander-prefs-confirmation\"/>."
