#. (itstool) path: sect2/para
#: C/index.docbook:7034
msgid "The menu for user actions and associated keyboard shortcuts can be opened by clicking on <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Keyboard Shortcuts...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Below, the usage of the dialog is <guimenuitem>Keyboard Shortcuts...</guimenuitem> explained."
